## Enforcement

### Pre-Creation Checks

**Before creating any document file**:
1. ✅ Verify document will have complete content
2. ✅ Check all required inputs are available
3. ✅ Ensure proper citations can be included (if AI-generated)
4. ✅ Confirm all sections can be filled

**If any check fails**: **Do NOT create the file.**

### Post-Creation Validation

**After creating a document**:
1. ✅ Verify file contains substantive content
2. ✅ Check all required sections are present
3. ✅ Validate citations are included (if AI-generated)
4. ✅ Ensure file is not just a placeholder

**If validation fails**: **Delete the file and regenerate when ready.**

